data.description: On a large corner lot, this delightful one-story house provides a cozy yet convenient living environment, ideal for those in search of a peaceful home. With three spacious bedrooms and two stylish bathrooms, this home caters to both family living and hosting guests. Upon entering, you're greeted by an open and airy layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal environment for gatherings and everyday life. Large windows ensure ample natural light, enhancing the warmth and welcoming atmosphere throughout the home. The kitchen, equipped with modern appliances and ample counter space is the heart of the home. For outdoor enthusiasts and travelers, this property stands out with its thoughtfully installed RV hookups.. See ''more'' including electricity, sewer, and water connections, offering convenience for RV owners or guests. The expansive corner lot provides an outdoor space for gardening, leisure, and hosting gatherings, making it a versatile haven for all lifestyles. Whether you're enjoying the tranquility of the neighborhood or exploring the open road, this home is a perfect base for a life well-lived.
